# Static site (legacy)

The **vanilla `site/` HTML shell is not maintained** in this repo. Root `site/data/` may contain JSON status files only.

**Do not** add new static HTML/CSS/JS under `site/` unless a task explicitly rebuilds a static host.

For UX intent, use **`claude-design/`**. For Supabase read patterns from the removed Next app, see **`docs/DATA_READS_SPEC.md`**.
